        "title": "feat(ui): improve control UI chat and task UX",
        "body": "## Summary\nFocused PR extracting the UI improvements from the stalled #65258. The original PR had fallen 10,598 commits behind main.\n\n### Changes\n- **Grouped chat rendering** with tool card summaries and collapse/expand\n- **Tool cards** with timeline view, raw output toggle, and canvas preview in sidebar\n- **Exec-approval view** with improved layout and states  \n- **Markdown sidebar** with rich content display\n- **Chat view** improvements with grouped message rendering\n- **App-render and app-gateway** improvements for better chat UX\n- **Login gate** component\n- **App-view-state** for improved chat/task UI state management\n\n### Files changed (24 UI files)\n- `ui/src/ui/chat/tool-cards.ts` + test\n- `ui/src/ui/chat/grouped-render.ts`\n- `ui/src/ui/views/chat.ts` + test\n- `ui/src/ui/views/exec-approval.ts` + test\n- `ui/src/ui/views/login-gate.ts`, `markdown-sidebar.ts`\n- `ui/src/ui/app-render.ts`, `app-render.helpers.ts`, `app.ts`\n- `ui/src/ui/app-gateway.ts` + node test\n- `ui/src/ui/app-tool-stream.ts` + node test\n- `ui/src/ui/app-view-state.ts`, `sidebar-content.ts`\n- `ui/src/ui/types/chat-types.ts`\n- CSS: `ui/src/styles/chat/{grouped,layout,tool-cards}.css`, `components.css`, `layout.css`\n\n### Note\nSkipped `chat-spaces.ts` (network timeout fetching from original PR commit).\n\n### UI Proof / Mockup Preview\n![openclaw_ui_preview](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/aayushprsingh/openclaw/ui/chat-task-ux-improvements/assets/openclaw_ui_preview.png)\n",
